<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/6920096/annotation">共<span property="v:count">9</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="16297439">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zuogy/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1019831-33.jpg" alt="左思" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16297439/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16297439/" class="">第13篇</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zuogy/" class=" " title="左思">左思</a>
                (http://www.weibo.com/zuogy)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16297439">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">1、宋朝的市场经济（P330）：宋高宗就曾办举商业，说道：“市舶之利最厚，若措置得宜，所得动以百万计，岂不胜取之于民？”宋朝都城杭州有句民间俗语说：“东方的菜，西方的水，南方的柴，北方的米。”

2、伏尔泰（Francois-Marie Arouet）哲学通信与《国富论》类似的话（P332）：倘若步入比很多宫庭还要庄严的伦敦交易所，你就会看到各国代表为追求人类利益而聚在一起。在这里，犹太人、伊斯兰教徒和基督徒互相打交道，好像他..</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16297439/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-01-18 14:57</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                1、宋朝的市场经济（P330）：<blockquote><q>宋高宗就曾办举商业，说道：“市舶之利最厚，若措置得宜，所得动以百万计，岂不胜取之于民？”宋朝都城杭州有句民间俗语说：“东方的菜，西方的水，南方的柴，北方的米。”</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2、伏尔泰（Francois-Marie Arouet）哲学通信与《国富论》类似的话（P332）：<blockquote><q>倘若步入比很多宫庭还要庄严的伦敦交易所，你就会看到各国代表为追求人类利益而聚在一起。在这里，犹太人、伊斯兰教徒和基督徒互相打交道，好像他们信奉着同一宗教，在他们眼中，唯有那些破产者才被看做异教徒。在交易所中，长老会教徒会信赖再洗礼派教徒，而英国圣公会信徒也会相信贵格会教徒的许诺。而一旦离开这些和平而自由的集会，参会者中有些人人前往犹太教堂，而其他人也许会找酒喝；这位可能要以圣父、圣子、圣灵名义在圣盆中接受洗礼；那位可能要请人为他儿子行割礼，并为小孩儿含糊地诵读些让他都听不懂的希伯莱经文；而还有些人则戴着帽子赶往教堂，静候上帝的灵感；所有这些人都是心满意足的。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>备份：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>首先强烈推荐这本书中的一篇文章：Twenty Myths about Markets，这是我至今读到的有关市场作用最全面、浅显的表述：<a rel="nofollow" href="http://tomgpalmer.com/wp-content/uploads/papers/myths_about_markets_ii.pdf" target="_blank">http://tomgpalmer.com/wp-content/uploads/papers/myths_about_markets_ii.pdf</a>
亚马逊美国的评论“Palmer's exposition of ideas is well-researched, cleverly presented, unpretentious, and well balanced. His prose is amazing, articulate, concise, and humorous. For example, the chapter &quot;Twenty Myths about Markets&quot; is a model of a straightforward and persuasive writing. ”<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>这本书删节比较厉害，译者应该交代一下。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>和Kindle版对照，中文译本缺少kindle版的以下内容。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>第一部分“理论”，没有删节<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>第二部分“历史”，删除了两篇文章<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1）11篇：Classical liberalism, Marxism, and the conflict of classes: the classical liberal theory of class conflict<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2）14篇，why socialism collapsed in eastern Europe:<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.cato.org/special/berlinwall/palmer1990.html" target="_blank">http://www.cato.org/special/berlinwall/palmer1990.html</a><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>第三部分“实践”部分删得只剩下一篇文章，删除的文章如下<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1）15篇：Madison and Multiculturalism: Group representation, group rights, and consitutionalism<a rel="nofollow" href="http://tomgpalmer.com/wp-content/uploads/papers/madison-and-multiculturalism.pdf" target="_blank">http://tomgpalmer.com/wp-content/uploads/papers/madison-and-multiculturalism.pdf</a><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2）17篇：Infrastructure: public or private?<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>3）18篇：future schlock: government planning for tomorrow<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>4) 19篇：against taxes<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>5）20篇：Hothouse of hate<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>6）21篇：Census 2000: You may already be a winner!<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>7）22篇：The Egyptian Judiciary blazing the path to democracy and economic development<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>8）23篇：The &quot;crime&quot; of blogging in Egypt<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>9）24篇：Six facts about Iraq<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>10）25篇：Moscow's pride and prejudice<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>11）26篇：Chanllenges of democratization<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>第四部分：书与观念<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1）27篇：The literature of liberty<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2）28篇：With friends like this: review of Wealth and Poverty<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>3）33篇：Liberal flagship turns 70, Burning the midnight oil
