      <li style="border: none">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/link2/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fipac.library.sh.cn%2Fipac20%2Fipac.jsp%3Faspect%3Dbasic_search%26profile%3Dsl%26index%3DISBN%26term%3D9787511824493&amp;subject=7511824498&amp;type=borrow&amp;library=10012&amp;link2key=493dacf0ed" target="_blank">上海市中心图书馆(3)</a>
